---
<section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative Elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-0 w-72 h-72 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-x-1/2"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <span class="text-accent font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Kolay Süreç</span>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mt-3 mb-6">Nasıl Hizmet Alırım?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">Sağlığınıza kavuşmak için karmaşık prosedürlerle uğraşmayın. Sadece 3 adımda yanınızdayız.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
        <!-- Connecting Line (Desktop) -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-1/2 left-4 right-4 h-0.5 bg-gray-200 -translate-y-1/2 z-0 transform -mt-8"></div>
        
        <!-- Connecting Line (Mobile) -->
        <div class="lg:hidden absolute top-4 bottom-4 left-8 w-0.5 bg-gray-200 z-0"></div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-8">
            
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="relative group">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 relative z-10 lg:hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <!-- Number Watermark -->
                    <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-4 text-9xl font-bold text-gray-50 opacity-50 z-0 font-serif group-hover:text-blue-50 transition-colors select-none">1</div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-col lg:items-center text-left lg:text-center gap-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                             <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Bize Ulaşın</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                Çağrı merkezimizi arayın veya WhatsApp butonuna tıklayarak şikayetinizi kısaca belirtin.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
             <div class="relative group mt-8 lg:mt-0">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 relative z-10 lg:hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <!-- Number Watermark -->
                    <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-4 text-9xl font-bold text-gray-50 opacity-50 z-0 font-serif group-hover:text-amber-50 transition-colors select-none">2</div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-col lg:items-center text-left lg:text-center gap-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-amber-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/30 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-3 group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">Hemen Planlayalım</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                Konumunuza en yakın mobil sağlık ekibimizi yönlendirelim. Ortalama 45 dakikada yanınızdayız.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
             <div class="relative group mt-8 lg:mt-0">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 relative z-10 lg:hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <!-- Number Watermark -->
                    <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-4 text-9xl font-bold text-gray-50 opacity-50 z-0 font-serif group-hover:text-green-50 transition-colors select-none">3</div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-col lg:items-center text-left lg:text-center gap-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-emerald-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/30 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                             <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-3 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">Tedavi Olun</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                Uzman hekimimiz sizi muayene etsin, gerekli tedaviyi uygulayıp ilaçlarınızı düzenlesin.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
